WEBVTT

00:00:02.180 --> 00:00:04.900
&lrm;<i>In the daytime, I'm Marinette.</i>

00:00:04.980 --> 00:00:07.980
&lrm;<i>Just a normal girl with a normal life.</i>

00:00:08.060 --> 00:00:10.860
&lrm;<i>But there's something about me</i>
&lrm;<i>that no one knows yet.</i>

00:00:10.940 --> 00:00:12.460
&lrm;<i>Because I have a secret.</i>

00:00:13.460 --> 00:00:15.780
&lrm;<i>♪ Miraculous! Simply the best! ♪</i>

00:00:16.220 --> 00:00:18.780
&lrm;<i>♪ Up to the test when things go wrong! ♪</i>

00:00:19.140 --> 00:00:21.540
&lrm;<i>♪ Miraculous! The luckiest! ♪</i>

00:00:21.700 --> 00:00:24.380
&lrm;<i>♪ The power of love, always so strong! ♪</i>

00:00:24.620 --> 00:00:27.260
&lrm;<i>♪ Miraculous! ♪</i>

00:00:29.340 --> 00:00:32.180
&lrm;<i>♪ Main theme ♪</i>

00:00:32.260 --> 00:00:33.460
&lrm;[Mumbling]

00:00:33.900 --> 00:00:36.540
&lrm;Mr Stone would like his breakfast
&lrm;on the back of a polar bear.

00:00:36.620 --> 00:00:38.260
&lrm;-Could you arrange that for me?
&lrm;-[JAGGED STONE]: Fetch!

00:00:38.340 --> 00:00:40.020
&lrm;-Uh...
&lrm;[phone ringing]

00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:42.620
&lrm;I'll see what I can do, Miss Penny.
&lrm;Will that be all?

00:00:43.100 --> 00:00:44.820
&lrm;Yes, a red-eye flight would be preferable.

00:00:45.100 --> 00:00:47.260
&lrm;Jagged's crocodile, Fang,
&lrm;hates flying in the daytime.

00:00:47.340 --> 00:00:50.020
&lrm;I found the way to market his album.

00:00:50.380 --> 00:00:52.380
&lrm;He'll be a guest on a reality TV show!

00:00:52.500 --> 00:00:54.660
&lrm;I don't think Jagged will be OK with --

00:00:54.740 --> 00:00:57.300
&lrm;No, I wasn't talking with you.
&lrm;Confirm that flight.

00:00:57.380 --> 00:00:59.020
&lrm;Thanks a lot! I'll call you back!

00:00:59.100 --> 00:00:59.940
&lrm;Bob, wait.

00:01:00.020 --> 00:01:02.420
&lrm;Penny, did you remember to order
&lrm;macaroons for Fang?

00:01:02.740 --> 00:01:05.140
&lrm;I'm taking care of that right now.

00:01:05.220 --> 00:01:06.780
&lrm;[knock on door]

00:01:08.220 --> 00:01:11.140
&lrm;Your album's gonna go platinum.
&lrm;Wait till you find out how!

00:01:11.580 --> 00:01:14.340
&lrm;I'm sorry, Miss Penny,
&lrm;but you cannot allow your crocodile

00:01:14.460 --> 00:01:17.780
&lrm;-to just roam around the hotel by itself!
&lrm;-I'm sorry, Mr Bourgeois.

00:01:17.860 --> 00:01:19.140
&lrm;[phone rings]

00:01:19.220 --> 00:01:21.260
&lrm;Yes. What?

00:01:21.340 --> 00:01:24.060
&lrm;-[JAGGED STONE]: What? What is this trash?
&lrm;-Thanks, Mr Mayor.

00:01:24.140 --> 00:01:26.700
&lrm;You want me to be a guest
&lrm;on&lrm;<i> Rocker Wants A Wife?</i>

00:01:26.780 --> 00:01:28.660
&lrm;There's nothing rock'n'roll
&lrm;about that show!

00:01:28.740 --> 00:01:31.420
&lrm;-My fans will never watch it!
&lrm;-Of course they will.

00:01:31.500 --> 00:01:34.100
&lrm;-This is how marketing works these days!
&lrm;-No way!

00:01:34.180 --> 00:01:37.420
&lrm;-I'm a genuine rock'n'roller, Bob!
&lrm;-I am so sorry, Miss.

00:01:37.500 --> 00:01:41.300
&lrm;There were no polar bears available.
&lrm;Would a pony do, instead?

00:01:41.380 --> 00:01:43.540
&lrm;[JAGGED STONE]:
&lrm;I can dig being a guest on a reality show,

00:01:43.620 --> 00:01:45.740
&lrm;but it's gotta be music to my ears.

00:01:45.820 --> 00:01:48.140
&lrm;-Quality!
&lrm;-A pony is fine.

00:01:48.220 --> 00:01:51.020
&lrm;Can you throw in some macaroons too,
&lrm;please? Thanks.

00:01:51.300 --> 00:01:54.940
&lrm;No, not you. Don't worry, there won't be
&lrm;any ponies... just a crocodile!

00:01:55.020 --> 00:01:58.420
&lrm;[BOB]: Deal with it! You will be a guest
&lrm;on that show, whether you like it or not!

00:01:58.620 --> 00:02:00.940
&lrm;Oh, yeah?
&lrm;And how're you gonna make me do that?

00:02:01.020 --> 00:02:02.660
&lrm;-I think we're done here, Bob.
&lrm;-Psst...

00:02:02.740 --> 00:02:04.180
&lrm;[whispers]

00:02:06.700 --> 00:02:09.780
&lrm;Of course! Now that's what I call
&lrm;a rock'n'roll idea!

00:02:09.860 --> 00:02:12.340
&lrm;Penny, you're the best!
&lrm;What would I do without you?

00:02:12.420 --> 00:02:14.060
&lrm;[she sighs]
&lrm;<i>♪ violins ♪</i>

00:02:14.180 --> 00:02:17.340
&lrm;<i>♪ rock music ♪</i>

00:02:17.420 --> 00:02:20.100
&lrm;[crowd cheering]

00:02:27.700 --> 00:02:31.100
&lrm;<i>Welcome to </i>&lrm;Fill my Shoes&lrm;<i>!</i>
&lrm;<i>You're joining us live on a new episode</i>

00:02:31.180 --> 00:02:34.180
&lrm;<i>and our guest today</i>
&lrm;<i>is the one and only Jagged Stone!</i>

00:02:34.260 --> 00:02:36.620
&lrm;<i>Rock'n'roll! Yeah!</i>

00:02:36.700 --> 00:02:39.980
&lrm;<i>-Filling the shoes of... a baker!</i>
&lrm;<i>-Yo, rockers!</i>

00:02:40.300 --> 00:02:42.860
&lrm;<i>A big thanks to Tom Dupain</i>
&lrm;<i>for having us in his bakery,</i>

00:02:42.940 --> 00:02:44.820
&lrm;<i>the best in Paris, I might add!</i>

00:02:44.900 --> 00:02:45.780
&lrm;[chuckles]

00:02:46.220 --> 00:02:48.060
&lrm;<i>Uh... Hello!</i>

00:02:49.020 --> 00:02:51.940
&lrm;Excuse me. Would you like
&lrm;some hot croissants?

00:02:53.420 --> 00:02:56.820
&lrm;I'm not sure it was a good idea
&lrm;to let them film the show here, sweetie!

00:02:56.900 --> 00:03:00.300
&lrm;Of course it was, Mom!
&lrm;Jagged asked specifically to come here.

00:03:00.380 --> 00:03:02.660
&lrm;You realise how good
&lrm;it'll be for the bakery?

00:03:02.740 --> 00:03:04.900
&lrm;And Dad will become an instant celebrity!

00:03:04.980 --> 00:03:07.420
&lrm;Well, for a celebrity,
&lrm;he looks pretty nervous.

00:03:08.580 --> 00:03:09.460
&lrm;No, no!

00:03:09.820 --> 00:03:11.260
&lrm;<i>You have the right energy, Jagged,</i>

00:03:11.380 --> 00:03:13.540
&lrm;<i>you just need to be gentle.</i>

00:03:13.620 --> 00:03:15.300
&lrm;<i>Hi. More like this!</i>

00:03:15.460 --> 00:03:17.900
&lrm;-Grr!
&lrm;-Calm down, Fang!

00:03:19.020 --> 00:03:22.340
&lrm;-Are you OK, Miss Penny?
&lrm;-Yes. It's just this show was my idea

00:03:22.420 --> 00:03:26.500
&lrm;and Jagged's putting all his trust in me.
&lrm;I just hope everything goes well today.

00:03:26.740 --> 00:03:29.180
&lrm;<i>So, how does it feel</i>
&lrm;<i>to fill the baker's shoes today?</i>

00:03:29.260 --> 00:03:32.420
&lrm;<i>It's awesome! Check out this edible guitar</i>
&lrm;<i>I made from scratch!</i>

00:03:32.500 --> 00:03:33.860
&lrm;<i>This is so rock'n'roll!</i>

00:03:34.020 --> 00:03:36.420
&lrm;<i>♪ Flour, eggs and butter ♪</i>

00:03:37.260 --> 00:03:38.260
&lrm;[chuckles]

00:03:38.340 --> 00:03:42.100
&lrm;So, Miss Penny, what's it like working
&lrm;with a star like Jagged? He seems so cool!

00:03:42.180 --> 00:03:44.620
&lrm;Oh, yes, he's... wonderful!

00:03:45.540 --> 00:03:48.380
&lrm;Uh, I mean... Yeah, he's awesome!

00:03:49.860 --> 00:03:53.900
&lrm;<i>♪ Flour, eggs and butter</i>
&lrm;<i>and fire in the oven ♪</i>

00:03:53.980 --> 00:03:57.860
&lrm;Oh, Come on! Are you gonna finally
&lrm;put cheese on that bread or what?

00:03:57.940 --> 00:04:00.060
&lrm;Since when are you interested
&lrm;in this show?

00:04:00.140 --> 00:04:05.220
&lrm;-The show's being shot at Marinette's.
&lrm;<i>-♪ This is the bakers' rock'n'roll ♪</i>

00:04:05.300 --> 00:04:08.660
&lrm;<i>Yo, Marinette! My favourite little lady!</i>
&lrm;<i>Come over rock out with us!</i>

00:04:08.740 --> 00:04:10.740
&lrm;<i>Uh...</i>&lrm; [giggles]

00:04:13.940 --> 00:04:16.140
&lrm;<i>It's so cool we get</i>
&lrm;<i>to spend the day together!</i>

00:04:16.220 --> 00:04:17.860
&lrm;<i>Marinette's really talented.</i>

00:04:17.940 --> 00:04:20.860
&lrm;<i>She did the artwork for my album</i>
&lrm;<i>and she's only in high school!</i>

00:04:21.220 --> 00:04:24.780
&lrm;<i>Wow! Impressive! A true family of artists.</i>
&lrm;<i>A talented young designer</i>

00:04:24.860 --> 00:04:28.860
&lrm;<i>and a gifted pâtissier. By the way,</i>
&lrm;<i>what are you gonna bake for us, Tom?</i>

00:04:28.940 --> 00:04:32.580
&lrm;<i>How about some chocolate croissants?</i>
&lrm;<i>Can you grab a bag of flour, please?</i>

00:04:32.940 --> 00:04:34.060
&lrm;<i>Sure, Dad.</i>

00:04:34.140 --> 00:04:35.980
&lrm;<i>Oh! Yes!</i>

00:04:37.300 --> 00:04:38.620
&lrm;<i>Uh-oh.</i>

00:04:39.700 --> 00:04:43.660
&lrm;<i>Hey, look! I look like a ghost!</i>
&lrm;<i>Rock'n'Boo-hoo! Ha, ha, ha, ha!</i>

00:04:44.060 --> 00:04:46.460
&lrm;<i>Making pastries</i>
&lrm;<i>is obviously no piece of cake!</i>

00:04:46.540 --> 00:04:48.660
&lrm;<i>Stay tuned. We'll be back after the break!</i>

00:04:48.940 --> 00:04:49.860
&lrm;<i>Boo!</i>

00:04:49.940 --> 00:04:51.140
&lrm;And cut!

00:04:52.900 --> 00:04:55.500
&lrm;-Hi, Bob.
&lrm;-Alec! This is starting out very well!

00:04:55.660 --> 00:04:58.020
&lrm;-Sorry, Jagged.
&lrm;-No sweat, Marinette.

00:04:58.100 --> 00:05:00.780
&lrm;-Could you tell me where the restroom is?
&lrm;-Upstairs.

00:05:00.860 --> 00:05:02.300
&lrm;Thanks.

00:05:02.380 --> 00:05:04.900
&lrm;Come on, we have some cleaning up to do.

00:05:05.700 --> 00:05:09.460
&lrm;-[PENNY]: Are you sure it's up here?
&lrm;-[JAGGED STONE]: She said upstairs.

00:05:12.420 --> 00:05:14.420
&lrm;Wait. This isn't the restroom.

00:05:14.500 --> 00:05:17.940
&lrm;This must be Marinette's bedroom. Cool.
&lrm;Hey, there's a sink!

00:05:18.780 --> 00:05:22.460
&lrm;-Our rating are sky high!
&lrm;-Alec, we're back in 30 seconds!

00:05:22.540 --> 00:05:24.620
&lrm;-Where's Jagged?
&lrm;-Upstairs.

00:05:24.940 --> 00:05:26.820
&lrm;Thanks! Follow me! We'll improvise!

00:05:28.740 --> 00:05:32.980
&lrm;Hey, look! Man!
&lrm;Marinette's got some serious talent!

00:05:33.780 --> 00:05:36.740
&lrm;Hey! I know this guy!

00:05:36.820 --> 00:05:40.340
&lrm;-Rock on, Jagged!
&lrm;-We've got to hurry, Jagged.

00:05:40.420 --> 00:05:42.980
&lrm;Yeah, yeah! Relax, Penny.

00:05:43.060 --> 00:05:46.300
&lrm;He's here! Come on, start shooting!
&lrm;In three, two, one...

00:05:46.620 --> 00:05:49.900
&lrm;<i>We're back on the air with Jagged Stone,</i>
&lrm;<i>filling the shoes of a baker!</i>

00:05:49.980 --> 00:05:53.940
&lrm;<i>Let's see how this rock star</i>
&lrm;<i>cleans off all that flour!</i>

00:05:54.020 --> 00:05:56.380
&lrm;<i>Hey, there are more photos of this dude</i>
&lrm;<i>than of me!</i>

00:05:56.460 --> 00:05:58.940
&lrm;<i>I think the baker's daughter's</i>
&lrm;<i>got a little crush!</i>

00:06:01.380 --> 00:06:03.900
&lrm;Lookie there. Another secret admirer.

00:06:03.980 --> 00:06:06.340
&lrm;[JAGGED STONE]:
&lrm;<i>Oh! Teenage love is so sweet!</i>

00:06:06.420 --> 00:06:10.780
&lrm;<i>-Makes me wanna wrote a song!</i>
&lrm;-[gasps] No, no, no, no, no, no!

00:06:11.580 --> 00:06:14.100
&lrm;-Marinette?
&lrm;-No, no, no, no, no!

00:06:14.180 --> 00:06:16.860
&lrm;Keep calm, Marinette, it's not a big deal!

00:06:17.060 --> 00:06:19.820
&lrm;Of course it is! This is a major disaster!

00:06:19.900 --> 00:06:22.900
&lrm;I told everyone to watch today's show,
&lrm;including Adrien!

00:06:22.980 --> 00:06:25.700
&lrm;He'll see the photos
&lrm;and figure out I'm in love with him!

00:06:25.780 --> 00:06:28.780
&lrm;-But isn't that what you want?
&lrm;-No! Not like this!

00:06:29.500 --> 00:06:33.220
&lrm;-What are you guys doing in here?
&lrm;-I'm sorry. I couldn't find the restroom!

00:06:33.300 --> 00:06:35.980
&lrm;Hey, Marinette!
&lrm;You want me to sign this poster of me?

00:06:36.700 --> 00:06:40.700
&lrm;<i>No! I just need everyone to leave!</i>
&lrm;<i>And you, stop filming!</i>

00:06:40.780 --> 00:06:43.660
&lrm;<i>-Penny, do something!</i>
&lrm;<i>-You heard the lady!</i>

00:06:46.100 --> 00:06:48.940
&lrm;<i>Security and Comfort...</i>

00:06:49.740 --> 00:06:51.820
&lrm;Hey, Penny! You just cut us off the air!

00:06:53.060 --> 00:06:54.700
&lrm;-Sorry.
&lrm;-No, Penny.

00:06:54.780 --> 00:06:58.340
&lrm;-Get them out of here first, please!
&lrm;-Give me that cable. We're live!

00:06:58.420 --> 00:07:01.180
&lrm;Atchoo! Penny, was that flour organic?

00:07:01.260 --> 00:07:03.340
&lrm;I'm allergic to non-organic flour!

00:07:03.420 --> 00:07:06.060
&lrm;-Penny, the cable!
&lrm;-We've got no picture!

00:07:06.340 --> 00:07:08.100
&lrm;Penny! Do you have a tissue?

00:07:08.180 --> 00:07:09.380
&lrm;-Atchoo!
&lrm;-[MARINETTE]: Penny, no!

00:07:09.460 --> 00:07:11.180
&lrm;Get out of my room first!

00:07:11.260 --> 00:07:12.540
&lrm;[BOB]: Penny, what is going on?

00:07:12.620 --> 00:07:14.580
&lrm;[ALEC]:
&lrm;You said this gig would be easy as pie!

00:07:14.700 --> 00:07:20.620
&lrm;Stop! That's enough! All of you
&lrm;back downstairs! Now! Out, out, out!

00:07:23.780 --> 00:07:25.620
&lrm;Out, out, out!

00:07:25.900 --> 00:07:28.500
&lrm;-What do we do now?
&lrm;-I'll meet you downstairs in five.

00:07:28.700 --> 00:07:32.100
&lrm;-But, Penny...
&lrm;-In five!

00:07:36.100 --> 00:07:43.100
&lrm;<i>♪ Dramatic music ♪</i>

00:07:44.420 --> 00:07:48.580
&lrm;A devoted assistant losing her cool.
&lrm;Such a fortunate opportunity.

00:07:57.140 --> 00:08:00.900
&lrm;Fly away, my little akuma,
&lrm;and evilise her!

00:08:12.060 --> 00:08:15.220
&lrm;Troublemaker, I am Hawk Moth.

00:08:15.300 --> 00:08:17.140
&lrm;You've always been the faithful one,

00:08:17.220 --> 00:08:20.500
&lrm;taking care of other people
&lrm;and solving all their problems.

00:08:20.580 --> 00:08:22.980
&lrm;Today, you are free of that burden!

00:08:23.060 --> 00:08:27.340
&lrm;From now on, you shall be the creator
&lrm;of all their problems!

00:08:28.180 --> 00:08:30.820
&lrm;Sounds like a plan, Hawk Moth!

00:08:40.580 --> 00:08:42.420
&lrm;So, what's next on my to-do list?

00:08:42.500 --> 00:08:45.500
&lrm;Oh, I know. Taking care of Jagged.

00:08:45.580 --> 00:08:47.620
&lrm;[evil laugh]

00:08:52.380 --> 00:08:55.540
&lrm;I'll be a laughing stock at school,
&lrm;online... all over town!

00:08:55.620 --> 00:08:58.060
&lrm;And Adrien will never talk to me again!

00:08:58.140 --> 00:09:00.940
&lrm;This is a disaster,
&lrm;a disaster, a disaster, a disaster!

00:09:01.020 --> 00:09:04.180
&lrm;-Just breathe! Everything's gonna be OK.
&lrm;-It is?

00:09:04.260 --> 00:09:07.820
&lrm;Yeah! Besides, it's too late anyway.
&lrm;The show's live!

00:09:11.460 --> 00:09:16.060
&lrm;Oh, no! This is a disaster, a disaster,
&lrm;a disaster, a disaster, a disaster!

00:09:16.580 --> 00:09:19.660
&lrm;All right, everyone back to work!
&lrm;Chop, chop!

00:09:19.740 --> 00:09:24.780
&lrm;OK, people! Jagged, Mr Dupain, get back
&lrm;to your place. We're live in five, four...

00:09:25.380 --> 00:09:26.820
&lrm;-three...
&lrm;-Wait, wait, wait.

00:09:27.060 --> 00:09:30.340
&lrm;-We'd rather not continue.
&lrm;-What? Have you lost your mind?

00:09:30.420 --> 00:09:34.220
&lrm;We're not comfortable with your cameras
&lrm;invading our privacy.

00:09:34.300 --> 00:09:36.620
&lrm;Our daughter is upset
&lrm;because of your show.

00:09:36.700 --> 00:09:39.220
&lrm;-We won't allow that!
&lrm;-The ratings are sky high!

00:09:39.340 --> 00:09:42.060
&lrm;There's no way we stop the show now.
&lrm;Right, Jagged?

00:09:42.140 --> 00:09:44.020
&lrm;Atchoo!

00:09:44.860 --> 00:09:47.420
&lrm;-Ah-ha! See?
&lrm;-Oh! How dare you?

00:09:48.860 --> 00:09:52.140
&lrm;<i>Ya! I demand an apology!</i>

00:09:52.660 --> 00:09:54.260
&lrm;Darling, what happened?

00:09:57.140 --> 00:09:59.020
&lrm;Hey, are you looking for trouble?

00:09:59.780 --> 00:10:00.860
&lrm;[nervous laugh]

00:10:01.220 --> 00:10:03.060
&lrm;<i>I could pretend</i>
&lrm;<i>that this isn't bothering me,</i>

00:10:03.140 --> 00:10:05.060
&lrm;<i>but now you've gone too far, Mister.</i>

00:10:05.140 --> 00:10:08.500
&lrm;-Dad?
&lrm;-Don't lay a finger on my husband!

00:10:11.060 --> 00:10:11.980
&lrm;-Huh!
&lrm;-Huh?

00:10:12.380 --> 00:10:14.900
&lrm;-Aaah!
&lrm;-[laughter]

00:10:15.540 --> 00:10:19.900
&lrm;No! What’s happening? A ghost!
&lrm;It's a ghost! Where's Penny? Penny!

00:10:25.620 --> 00:10:27.940
&lrm;<i>Are you sure your bakery</i>
&lrm;<i>ain't built on a cemetery?</i>

00:10:28.260 --> 00:10:29.580
&lrm;<i>Aaah!</i>

00:10:30.020 --> 00:10:31.060
&lrm;<i>Aaah!</i>

00:10:45.460 --> 00:10:48.100
&lrm;-Hello, Jagged!
&lrm;-Whoa!

00:10:48.180 --> 00:10:50.780
&lrm;Who are you? Where's Penny? Penny!

00:10:51.140 --> 00:10:54.900
&lrm;<i>There's no more Penny to deal</i>
&lrm;<i>with all your problems, Jagged!</i>

00:10:55.260 --> 00:10:57.900
&lrm;<i>From now on, there's only Troublemaker,</i>

00:10:58.820 --> 00:11:02.820
&lrm;<i>and I'll make your life</i>
&lrm;<i>nothing but problems!</i>&lrm; [evil laugh]

00:11:04.580 --> 00:11:08.260
&lrm;Aaah!

00:11:08.780 --> 00:11:11.300
&lrm;-Penny?
&lrm;-That poor Penny was trying so hard

00:11:11.380 --> 00:11:14.460
&lrm;to help everyone that she became
&lrm;a perfect victim for Hawk Moth!

00:11:14.540 --> 00:11:17.740
&lrm;Shooting the show here
&lrm;definitely wasn't a good idea!

00:11:18.100 --> 00:11:20.860
&lrm;Tikki, spots on! Yah!

