&lrm;<i>♪ Dance music ♪</i>

00:12:00.220 --> 00:12:02.500
&lrm;Here's come trouble again, Jagged!

00:12:02.580 --> 00:12:03.860
&lrm;Not in my bakery!

00:12:07.620 --> 00:12:08.700
&lrm;Penny, stop! It's...

00:12:08.780 --> 00:12:13.540
&lrm;-It's not... Atchoo... rock'n'roll!
&lrm;-I hate rock'n'roll, Jagged!

00:12:13.620 --> 00:12:16.940
&lrm;I only love chaos,
&lrm;and you'll be my number-one hit!

00:12:17.620 --> 00:12:20.980
&lrm;<i>You're witnessing the arrival</i>
&lrm;<i>of a new supervillain, live! Aaah!</i>

