&lrm;<i>Show's over, people!</i>

00:12:23.380 --> 00:12:24.900
&lrm;[evil laugh]

00:12:25.300 --> 00:12:28.300
&lrm;I am in front of Dupain-Cheng bakery,
&lrm;where a new villain appeared.

00:12:28.380 --> 00:12:31.980
&lrm;Hey, everyone, let me take care of this.
&lrm;It'll be a piece of cake.

00:12:40.220 --> 00:12:42.780
&lrm;-Catacly --
&lrm;-So, you wanna play "Rescue"?

00:12:42.940 --> 00:12:44.820
&lrm;No one's gonna be rescued today.

00:12:45.900 --> 00:12:47.100
&lrm;Aaah!

00:12:49.420 --> 00:12:50.860
&lrm;Woah!

00:12:50.980 --> 00:12:53.580
&lrm;Aaah!

00:12:54.220 --> 00:12:56.820
&lrm;-Right on time, Cat Noir!
&lrm;-Good to see you, Bugaboo.

00:12:56.900 --> 00:13:01.820
&lrm;-Looks like we'll break bread today.
&lrm;-Stop calling me Bugaboo! Follow me!

00:13:09.700 --> 00:13:12.180
&lrm;Oh, wow! That's a lot of pictures!

00:13:12.300 --> 00:13:14.540
&lrm;We can take the grand tour later,
&lrm;Cat Noir!

00:13:19.940 --> 00:13:21.620
&lrm;Whoa!

00:13:21.700 --> 00:13:22.580
&lrm;Sorry!

00:13:30.300 --> 00:13:31.740
&lrm;I said later, Cat Noir!

00:13:33.460 --> 00:13:34.500
&lrm;Aaah!

00:13:39.180 --> 00:13:40.660
&lrm;Look out!

00:13:47.820 --> 00:13:49.420
&lrm;The akuma is inside the pen!

00:13:52.420 --> 00:13:54.020
&lrm;Touch me if you dare!

00:13:55.620 --> 00:13:58.980
&lrm;What are we gonna do?
&lrm;I can't touch her with a ten-foot pole!

00:13:59.220 --> 00:14:01.060
&lrm;Her strength is also her weakness.

00:14:01.140 --> 00:14:04.220
&lrm;In order to touch us,
&lrm;she must become touchable herself!

00:14:06.500 --> 00:14:08.860
&lrm;Oh! Uh... There you are! All right!

00:14:13.380 --> 00:14:16.060
&lrm;Be careful.
&lrm;She's probably hiding in this room!

00:14:16.140 --> 00:14:17.580
&lrm;If she wants our Miraculous,

00:14:17.660 --> 00:14:20.100
&lrm;-she can't be untouchable.
&lrm;-If we can grab her,

00:14:20.180 --> 00:14:22.980
&lrm;-we can also grab her pen.
&lrm;-And capture the akuma.

00:14:23.100 --> 00:14:24.620
&lrm;But we'll have to act fast!

00:14:25.540 --> 00:14:26.860
&lrm;[evil laugh]

00:14:28.860 --> 00:14:30.780
&lrm;Gotcha!

00:14:38.060 --> 00:14:40.340
&lrm;You've already lost half the battle,
&lrm;Ladybug!

00:14:40.780 --> 00:14:41.660
&lrm;No!

00:14:43.060 --> 00:14:44.700
&lrm;Excellent, Troublemaker!

00:14:52.460 --> 00:14:54.260
&lrm;Cataclysm!

00:15:03.700 --> 00:15:04.900
&lrm;I had it!

00:15:11.980 --> 00:15:13.220
&lrm;That was a close call.

00:15:13.300 --> 00:15:16.340
&lrm;Certainly not how I dreamed
&lrm;we'd share our secret identity.

00:15:16.420 --> 00:15:18.220
&lrm;Oh, no. Not like that!

00:15:18.540 --> 00:15:22.060
&lrm;It'll all have to wait, at least until
&lrm;we kick Trouble's butt and Hawk Moth!

00:15:22.820 --> 00:15:24.340
&lrm;Lucky Charm!

00:15:29.740 --> 00:15:31.820
&lrm;A broken plate?

00:15:35.820 --> 00:15:38.380
&lrm;That's strange. I don't see how to use it!

00:15:38.460 --> 00:15:40.580
&lrm;Maybe losing an earring
&lrm;weakened your power?

00:15:41.420 --> 00:15:43.140
&lrm;My power has to be working!

00:15:45.500 --> 00:15:48.620
&lrm;It is working! Sticking time!

00:15:48.700 --> 00:15:49.580
&lrm;Seriously?

00:15:50.860 --> 00:15:53.020
&lrm;All right! We're coming to get you!

00:15:53.780 --> 00:15:57.380
&lrm;Be careful, Cat Noir. She can come
&lrm;from anywhere to get my Miraculous.

00:15:59.460 --> 00:16:02.380
&lrm;She's nowhere to be seen.
&lrm;I'll check on the roof. Stay here!

00:16:02.460 --> 00:16:06.500
&lrm;No, don't leave me alone!
&lrm;I only have a plate to defend myself.

00:16:06.580 --> 00:16:07.700
&lrm;[evil laugh]

00:16:12.500 --> 00:16:14.700
&lrm;-No, stop!
&lrm;-Bravo, Troublemaker!

00:16:14.780 --> 00:16:15.780
&lrm;Take her Miraculous!

00:16:17.300 --> 00:16:19.260
&lrm;-What?
&lrm;-Having some trouble?

00:16:19.500 --> 00:16:20.900
&lrm;Oh, my poor Bugaboo.

00:16:20.980 --> 00:16:24.300
&lrm;Another supervillain fan has literally
&lrm;glued themselves to you.

00:16:24.580 --> 00:16:27.580
&lrm;Sorry to disappoint,
&lrm;but I'm the only one to stick to Milady.

00:16:36.180 --> 00:16:37.220
&lrm;No!

00:16:39.180 --> 00:16:41.420
&lrm;No more evildoing for you, little akuma!

00:16:44.980 --> 00:16:47.140
&lrm;Time to de-evilise!

00:16:50.780 --> 00:16:52.100
&lrm;Gotcha!

00:16:52.860 --> 00:16:54.860
&lrm;Bye-bye, little butterfly.

00:16:55.260 --> 00:16:57.300
&lrm;Miraculous Ladybug!

00:17:01.340 --> 00:17:03.620
&lrm;[cheering]

00:17:08.900 --> 00:17:10.260
&lrm;What... ?

00:17:10.340 --> 00:17:13.900
&lrm;-What happened? Where's Jagged?
&lrm;-You're always so helpful,

00:17:13.980 --> 00:17:15.740
&lrm;putting everyone before you.

00:17:15.820 --> 00:17:18.900
&lrm;Let's worry about Penny for a change.
&lrm;How are you feeling?

00:17:21.140 --> 00:17:22.980
&lrm;I'm fine. Thank you, Ladybug.

00:17:24.540 --> 00:17:26.820
&lrm;Oops! We gotta a go! Rock'n'roll!

00:17:27.660 --> 00:17:28.820
&lrm;Rock'n'roll!

00:17:34.260 --> 00:17:36.300
&lrm;Phew! Well, that was a close call.

00:17:36.380 --> 00:17:38.900
&lrm;Looks like you won't find out
&lrm;my identity today.

00:17:38.980 --> 00:17:40.860
&lrm;-I already know who you are.
&lrm;-Huh?

00:17:41.820 --> 00:17:43.460
&lrm;You're the girl of my dreams!

00:17:44.580 --> 00:17:46.940
&lrm;[laughs] Silly Kitty!

00:17:48.340 --> 00:17:49.300
&lrm;-Pound it!
&lrm;-Pound it!

00:17:58.860 --> 00:17:59.980
&lrm;[laughs]

00:18:00.660 --> 00:18:02.660
&lrm;-Mom, Dad!
&lrm;-Marinette!

00:18:02.740 --> 00:18:04.460
&lrm;-Are you OK?
&lrm;-I'm fine.

00:18:04.540 --> 00:18:07.380
&lrm;I locked myself in the bathroom.

00:18:07.460 --> 00:18:09.620
&lrm;-Ahem!
&lrm;-Penny!

00:18:11.020 --> 00:18:13.980
&lrm;-Hi, everyone.
&lrm;-Penny!

00:18:15.740 --> 00:18:19.220
&lrm;Oh, Penny! I'm so glad to see you
&lrm;without your supervillain costume!

00:18:19.420 --> 00:18:21.940
&lrm;What would I do without you?
&lrm;You're the best!

00:18:36.380 --> 00:18:38.460
&lrm;-Have a nice day, sweetie!
&lrm;-Bye, Mom!

00:18:41.460 --> 00:18:42.500
&lrm;Are you OK, Marinette?

00:18:42.580 --> 00:18:46.100
&lrm;I'll never ever persuade my parents
&lrm;to shoot a show at our house again!

00:18:46.340 --> 00:18:49.460
&lrm;Not unless you want the whole world
&lrm;to know all of your secrets.

00:18:49.580 --> 00:18:51.700
&lrm;I need to stay on the down-low
&lrm;for a few days,

00:18:51.780 --> 00:18:55.860
&lrm;so everyone can forget all about
&lrm;what happened! Especially Adrien!

00:19:20.780 --> 00:19:23.820
&lrm;Phew! Hopefully, he didn't see me!

00:19:24.660 --> 00:19:26.140
&lrm;-Hey, Marinette!
&lrm;-Aaah!

00:19:26.220 --> 00:19:29.300
&lrm;How's it going? After what happened
&lrm;at your place last night,

00:19:29.380 --> 00:19:32.300
&lrm;-I was worried that --
&lrm;-Oh! So you watched the show, then!

00:19:32.380 --> 00:19:35.500
&lrm;Well... Uh, look,
&lrm;about what you saw on the show.

00:19:35.580 --> 00:19:38.180
&lrm;-The totographs in my room.
&lrm;-The photographs?

00:19:38.260 --> 00:19:39.660
&lrm;The grotographs, exactly!

00:19:39.740 --> 00:19:41.180
&lrm;It... it's not what you think!

00:19:42.700 --> 00:19:46.020
&lrm;See, I'm really into fashion and...

00:19:46.900 --> 00:19:48.660
&lrm;Are you lying?

00:19:49.380 --> 00:19:52.820
&lrm;No! I'm so not into you.
&lrm;I mean, sure, I'm interested in you...

00:19:52.900 --> 00:19:56.500
&lrm;but, um, not in that way.
&lrm;Well, you know! Ha, ha, ha, ha!

00:19:56.580 --> 00:19:59.660
&lrm;[chuckles] Just teasing!
&lrm;I understand, don't worry!

00:20:00.060 --> 00:20:04.260
&lrm;I've got used to having lots of fans
&lrm;and photographs of me everywhere,

00:20:04.340 --> 00:20:06.540
&lrm;even in the most unlikely places.

00:20:06.620 --> 00:20:09.740
&lrm;As if someone would have a picture
&lrm;of you under a bed, right?

00:20:09.820 --> 00:20:13.180
&lrm;Yeah. I was wondering.
&lrm;Since you're into fashion so much,

00:20:13.260 --> 00:20:16.940
&lrm;-you could come watch my next photo shoot!
&lrm;-No way! For you?

00:20:17.020 --> 00:20:20.740
&lrm;-Peel... Meal... For real?
&lrm;-Honestly, it's pretty long and boring.

00:20:20.820 --> 00:20:23.940
&lrm;But if you were there, it would be
&lrm;more fun. What do you say?

00:20:24.020 --> 00:20:25.940
&lrm;Oh, wow, yes!

00:20:26.020 --> 00:20:28.180
&lrm;-Thank you, Adrien!
&lrm;-I'll keep you posted, then.

00:20:28.660 --> 00:20:29.860
&lrm;See you later, in class.

00:20:31.860 --> 00:20:34.140
&lrm;I'm glad to have you as one of my fans.

00:20:43.340 --> 00:20:45.780
&lrm;Relax, Marinette. You can breathe now.

00:20:47.060 --> 00:20:49.740
&lrm;He invited me to one of his photo shoots!

00:20:49.820 --> 00:20:51.220
&lrm;Yeah, that's awesome!

00:20:51.460 --> 00:20:55.660
&lrm;And you even managed to get
&lrm;some normal sentences out, too!

00:20:55.740 --> 00:20:59.460
&lrm;-Oh, come on! That's not funny!
&lrm;-You're totally right. It's not funny!

00:21:01.060 --> 00:21:03.460
&lrm;[laughter]

00:21:07.500 --> 00:21:08.940
